Welcome to your R journey!

# What is R and RStudio?

R is a programming language purpose-built for statistical analysis. RStudio is an Integrated Development Environment for R - essentially, it's a wrapper designed to give you a more user-friendly workspace compared to the R terminal, which is pretty terrible to work with.

# How can I download these applications onto my computer?

Follow [these instructions](https://rstudio-education.github.io/hopr/starting.html) to download both R and RStudio on your laptop.



